<span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 06, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tqa1714484099568.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tqa1714484099568.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tqa1714484099568.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tqa1714484099568\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Convert a string to a regex string.</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">$regex ( <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> {, <var class=\"keyword varname\">Flags</var> })</code></p>\n<p class=\"p\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">if (NAME1 = $regex(\"dog\", \"i\")...</code></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__section_ocj_hr2_gbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d957295e68\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mwc_jr2_gbc\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mwc_jr2_gbc__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mwc_jr2_gbc__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mwc_jr2_gbc__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mwc_jr2_gbc__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mwc_jr2_gbc__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mwc_jr2_gbc__entry__3\">String to convert to a regex string.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mwc_jr2_gbc__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Flags</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mwc_jr2_gbc__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mwc_jr2_gbc__entry__3\">Regex flags to apply:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__ul_yxv_5r2_gbc\">\n<li class=\"li\">i</li>\n</ul></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__section_kmg_xr2_gbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d957295e138\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Returns the regex string if successful, or an empty string if an error occurred. In\n\t\t\t\tthis case, <code class=\"ph codeph\">$procerror</code> contains a negative value identifying the\n\t\t\t\texact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__table_j2b_cs2_gbc\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <code class=\"ph codeph\">$procerror </code>Commonly Returned Following\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">$regex</code></span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__table_j2b_cs2_gbc__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__table_j2b_cs2_gbc__entry__2\">Error constant</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__table_j2b_cs2_gbc__entry__3\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_j2b_cs2_gbc__entry__1\">-1014</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_j2b_cs2_gbc__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_REGEXSTRING&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_j2b_cs2_gbc__entry__3\">The regex string is not valid.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_j2b_cs2_gbc__entry__1\">-1110</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_j2b_cs2_gbc__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_TOPIC&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_j2b_cs2_gbc__entry__3\">The topic is not valid.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_j2b_cs2_gbc__entry__1\">-1301</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_j2b_cs2_gbc__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_SYNTAX &gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_j2b_cs2_gbc__entry__3\">Syntax error.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__topic_d59742e1_d59743e1_d59744e1_d59745e1_d59746e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d957295e227\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__section_v55_ns2_gbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d957295e237\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">A regex string is a group of characters and regex codes enclosed in slash marks\n\t\t\t\t\t(<code class=\"ph codeph\">/</code>) that can be used to match a string with a particular regex\n\t\t\t\tpattern. If the argument Flags is omitted the regex string can only match a\n\t\t\t\tcase-sensitive string. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"myt1714308484693.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/myt1714308484693.html\" title=\"Uniface enables you to determine if the data in a string value matches a desired pattern using regex strings. A regex string is a regular expression enclosed in forward slashes (‘/’).\">Regex Strings for Pattern Matching</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$regex</span> converts String to a regex string. Typically, the regex\n\t\t\t\tstring is then used in logical expressions (such as <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">if</span>,\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">repeat</span>, or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">while</span> statements) to check\n\t\t\t\twhether a string matches the particular regex pattern.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__section_w5t_tt2_gbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d957295e273\">Flags</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Flags determine how characters and regex codes are treated when performing a\n\t\t\t\tpattern-matching search.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"5\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mk2_vt2_gbc\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Regex String Flags</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:20%\"/><col style=\"width:20%\"/><col style=\"width:20%\"/><col style=\"width:20%\"/><col style=\"width:20%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mk2_vt2_gbc__entry__1\">Flags</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mk2_vt2_gbc__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mk2_vt2_gbc__entry__3\">Example</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mk2_vt2_gbc__entry__4\">Resulting Regex String</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mk2_vt2_gbc__entry__5\">Matches</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mk2_vt2_gbc__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">i</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mk2_vt2_gbc__entry__2\">Case-insensitive search</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mk2_vt2_gbc__entry__3\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">$regex(“dog”, “i”)</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mk2_vt2_gbc__entry__4\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">/dog/i</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"tqa1714484099568__table_mk2_vt2_gbc__entry__5\"><p class=\"p\">dog</p>Dog<p class=\"p\">DOG</p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6814347\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6814347\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$regex Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 06, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Convert a string to a regex string. $regex ( String {, Flags }) Example: if (NAME1 = $regex(\"dog\", \"i\")... Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description String String String to convert to a regex string. Flags String Regex flags to apply: i Return Values Returns the regex string if successful, or an empty string if an error occurred. In this case, $procerror contains a negative value identifying the exact error. Table 2. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $regex Value Error constant Meaning -1014 <UPROCERR_REGEXSTRING> The regex string is not valid. -1110 <UPROCERR_TOPIC> The topic is not valid. -1301 <UPROCERR_SYNTAX > Syntax error. Use Allowed in all component types. Description A regex string is a group of characters and regex codes enclosed in slash marks ( / ) that can be used to match a string with a particular regex pattern. If the argument Flags is omitted the regex string can only match a case-sensitive string. For more information, see Regex Strings for Pattern Matching . $regex converts String to a regex string. Typically, the regex string is then used in logical expressions (such as if , repeat , or while statements) to check whether a string matches the particular regex pattern. Flags Flags determine how characters and regex codes are treated when performing a pattern-matching search. Table 3. Regex String Flags Flags Meaning Example Resulting Regex String Matches i Case-insensitive search $regex(“dog”, “i”) /dog/i dog Dog DOG Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}